{"tid":783731,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大大力索自己啲臭屁真係好爽！！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2018-08-17T18:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T19:58:55.000Z","uid":98333,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"93611d319fe8248dd3eb6d4eb15072516b5506b9","tid":783731,"uid":98333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T18:17:28.000Z","msg":"放臭屁真係好爽！<br />\n自己聞自己啲屁，從來唔會覺得臭！<br />\n特別係陰啲陰啲，放好長既冇聲屁！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">爽！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">爽快！</span><br />\n<br />\n最鐘意個種<span style=\"color: gold;\">臭雞蛋味屁</span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係被豆到放，焗埋儲住佢！<br />\n放完塞個頭落去！<br />\n一次過大大力索！<br />\n爽啊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">濃烈而不刺鼻，</span><br />\n被一種只屬於自己既味道包圍住，<br />\n身心舒暢！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">爽！</span><br />\n最鐘意大大力索自己最臭個隻屁！<br />\n咩壓力都冇哂！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23562e502a91402f887e309e53a2f46a7326406","tid":783731,"uid":84953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T18:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e906d7f42046a52d5ce424bf168ea99bd0408a8b","tid":783731,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T18:19:22.000Z","msg":"黐撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7eaa3523134e895ffc13f6f59e64c921ea9b5c5","tid":783731,"uid":98333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f23562e502a91402f887e309e53a2f46a7326406","tid":783731,"uid":84953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T18:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img